00:59:03.970 --> 00:59:07.950
So it totally distorts the bargaining power.

00:59:07.950 --> 00:59:11.730
I tell my students "Think of another world
with a different set of rules.

00:59:11.730 --> 00:59:20.310
Let's assume that we have a set of rules that
capital couldn't move, but skilled labor could.

00:59:20.310 --> 00:59:23.830
